Ha nyau je ɗon nyaɗi timmi, nyauɗo ɗon mari larulaji kanduɗum be pofɗe, nawne ha nder ɓaandu fu, lammugo ko a nyammi, e iyam ɗaccatakke.
Nyauɓe je ɗon mari ɓaandu ɗon wula/mala mandolji pofɗe be wulugo ɓaandu be jaw, ko to foto fuffu sappinay hudure, sey larta viriis ngam lartol be wakati.
Ekkitol feere do ummatore ha desambre 2019 sappini yo'o limtol mandolji lati 98% je wulugo ɓaandu, 76% je sondaru joorɗum, 55% bana pofɗe daran, e 3% je caarol; 8% ha kunde nyauɓe mari no haaje mballol be hendu.
Irin sappinolji tawama ha nder ekkitolji keese didi bana ni je caalaje sammere e be sammere feere wangi gal raɓɓugo gal goɗɗo je sappinay nyau ngu.
Fahin bo'o, ekkitol ummatore feere ha 2012 sappini nyauɓe MERS-CoV ɗon no mari bo'o wulugo ɓaandu (98%), sondaru joorɗum (47%), be bana pofɗe daran (55%) bana aranol matinolji nyau maɓɓe.
Amma, 80% ha kunde maɓɓe mari haaje mbalol be hendu, ɓuri nyauɓe COVID-19 e ɗon tokkita be limtol mbarol MERS je ɓuri je COVID-19.
Caarol (26%) be daande je ɗon yoori (26%) wangini no ha nyauɓe MERS.
Ha nyauɓe SARS, ɗon sappini yo'o wulugo ɓaandu (99%-100%), sondaru joorɗum (29%-75%), pofɗe bana daran (40%-42%), caarol (20%-25%, be daande je ɗon yoori (13%-25%) lati arandere mandolji nyau e wallende be hendu emmotto gal nyauɓe 14%-20%.
